{"tid":1733661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"救POLY手足方法","createTime":"2019-11-18T07:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T07:34:10.000Z","uid":227921,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"65eb43a7a4b8e2f84cdf0ac86485225f5ddf29f9","tid":1733661,"uid":227921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"依家啲曱甴封哂紅磡啲路,<span style=\"color: red;\">明顯係想手足自己投降</span><br />\n佢地明顯唔想攻入POLY, 要攻一早攻入咗<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">而家係一個持久戰, 邊個捱得耐啲邊個就贏</span><br />\n佢地冇可能長期封住紅磡<br />\n所以而家可以做嘅就係<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">POLY手足:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">請保持體力同食物等待救援 如非必要唔好再嘗試突圍</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">繼續營救</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">和理非:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">發起和平抗爭 例如絕食 向世界求救</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">善用twitter對外宣傳</span>"},{"pid":"9ecca0921caaaa42488713c6e8457ac249694fde","tid":1733661,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beb2133ee1a3a258c38ceda80c1cd288e2cc26a0","tid":1733661,"uid":227921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:03:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cb6f6ffe601d694be236f8fb9dd77485d60d8c5","tid":1733661,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"和理非都要一齊圍"},{"pid":"4b910f4843ce405f4462509c433432d3d112a6c4","tid":1733661,"uid":227921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2629ee5560658c8c222033c2a26f2ca3cc06ee5a","tid":1733661,"uid":227921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f306dcc4415923267c2de86c5d0efb57831f0372","tid":1733661,"uid":227921,"like":0